creator: Netsky Tech
descriptionHtml:
Tincat Player is a lightweight player that supports most video formats.

* Beautiful UI
Tincat Player has a beautiful user interface, simple and elegant. Simple to use and supports night mode to protect your eyes.

* All Video Formats Support
Tincat Player not only has a beautiful UI, but also supports almost all video formats, including mp4, m3u8, flv, mpd, avi, rmvb and more.

* Gesture
Tincat Player also supports excellent gestures, you can adjust video progress, brightness, volume and more with one finger. You can also zoom the video with two fingers.

* Subtitle
Tincat Player also supports external subtitles. You can choose to add srt subtitles to the video for playback. If you do not have srt subtitles, Tincat Player also supports converting other formats of subtitles to srt subtitles.
